        List of items constituting the order.

        API reference

        Parameters:
        type - Optional. The type of this order item.Must be Type.Sku, Type.Tax, or Type.Shipping.
        amount - Optional. The amount (price) for this order item.
        currency - Optional. This currency of this order item. Required when amount is present.
        description - Optional. Human-readable description for this order item.
        parent - Optional. The ID of the SKU being ordered.
        quantity - Optional. The quantity of this order item. When type is Type.Sku, this is the number ofinstances of the SKU to be ordered.
